Package fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.solutions

package fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.solutions
Package containing modules allowing to return a homogenous type of data mining solutions for outside service to use.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app
    Core package containing all chocominer modules and features.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.solutions.arm
    Package containing association rule mining specific classes for solutions.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.solutions.im
    Package containing itemset mining specific classes for solutions.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.parsers
    Package containing parsers, which parse different types of external data structures from external libraries into a homogenous data structure and extract only the useful information from said data structures.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized
    This package is highly dependent on the SPMF library developed by Philippe Fournier Viger.
    fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.stats
    This package contains classes that provide useful statistics for the database the mining will be performed on.
  • Class
    Description
    PatternInterface
    Interface encompassing all homogenous pattern classes for different types of data mining such as Itemset Mining, Association Rule Mining, etc.
    Solutions<T extends PatternInterface>
    Object containing all the crucial information of a solved Data Mining Experience (ExperienceInterface) : A list of patterns that represent the solutions The amount of time the experience took to be solved The number of solutions The library used to solve the experience This solution object has a homogeneous structure which can be used and transformed into JSON by the API module of this application.
